reviewText: The seasons arrived in good quality save for one piece of broken plastic on the inside cover of one DVD case.  They run perfect and I am definitely pleased with the discount attributed to buying them together.
Excellent show! Very funny! Great price and excellent condition as promised by Amazon!
Delivered in time for Christmas. Just as I had hoped.
Repackaged and there was a punture and tear in one of the DVD cases. I rated 3 stars bc it was cheap but it was not new as described.

Really great price for two seasons! Definitely would suggest this set for those trying to collect all the seasons for a cheap price! One of my family members got hooked on this series and this set was amazing! I wish they made more sets like this!
This is one of a handful of shows that can make me laugh out loud! Brilliant!
Arrived on time, well packaged. Awesome seasons, as expected
Bought as a gift. The recipient lovedit
